0.60.1.1</para></item>
        <item><para>Update gettext dependency from 0.17 to
0.18.1.1</para></item>
        <item><para>Update libiconv dependency from 1.12 to
1.13.1</para></item>
        <item><para>Update openldap dependency from 2.4.12 to
2.4.26</para></item>
        <item><para>Update cyrus-sasl dependency from 2.1.22 to
2.1.25</para></item>
        <item><para>Update openssl dependency from 0.9.8h to
1.0.0e</para></item>
        <item><para>Remove support for HP-UX 10, AIX 4, SLES, RHEL
3</para></item>
      </change>

      <change date="2010 October 31" revision="2"
      author="Albert Chin-A-Young" email="china@thewrittenword.com">
        <item><para>Add support for RHEL 6</para></item>
      </change>
    </changelog>
  </program>
</programs>
